cId=3165432 |archivedate=2009-02-26 }}</ref>及其畫風<ref>{{cite web|url=http://goty.gamespy.com/2007/multiplayer/11.html |title=GameSpy Game of the Year 2007: Multiplayer |publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] |accessdate=2008-04-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080108065839/http://goty.gamespy.com/2007/multiplayer/11.html |archivedate=2008-01-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://goty.gamespy.com/2007/special/29.html |title=GameSpy's Game of the Year 2007: Special Awards |publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] |accessdate=2008-04-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200206/http://goty.gamespy.com/2007/special/29.html |archivedate=2013-10-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bestof.ign.com/2007/pc/12.html |title=IGN Best of 2007: PC - Best Artistic Design |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2008-02-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131117080859/http://bestof.ign.com/2007/pc/12.html |archivedate=2013-11-17 }}</ref>獲得多項獎項。且作為《橙盒》的成員之一，該遊戲也一併獲得很多雜誌的年度遊戲大獎。<ref name="AIAS">{{cite web|title=11th Annual Interactive Achievement Awards |publisher=[[Academy_of_Interactive_Arts_&_Sciences|AIAS]] |url=http://www.interactive.org/awards.php?winners&year=2008 |accessdate=2008-04-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080319003758/http://www.interactive.org/awards.php?winners&year=2008 |archivedate=2008-03-19 }}</ref><ref name="spike">{{cite web |title=Spike TV Announces 2007 'Video Game Awards' Winners |publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]] |date=2007-12-08 |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl?ACCT=104&STORY=/www/story/12-08-2007/0004719089&EDATE |accessdate=2008-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006183842/http://www2.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl?ACCT=104&STORY=%2Fwww%2Fstory%2F12-08-2007%2F0004719089&EDATE |archive-date=2012-10-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

